snippet.title: SSC | EP 01: First Attempt | Amit Bhadana
snippet.description:
Download Adda247 App: https://adda247.app.link/Amit_Bhadana_E1

Adda247, India's largest vernacular Exam preparation company founded in 2010. Adda247 provides well curated course content & teaching by top faculties of industry for all types of Exam preparations, i.e., Govt jobs, IIT, Medical, State Exams, etc.

Rate Us On IMDB: https://www.imdb.com/title/tt29424187/

SSC, vo exam jo lakhon students ki umeed hai aur kuch logon ke liye profitable business. Ye kahani hai SSC yani Shiv Shankar Chaudhary aur uski life ke 2 important phases ki. Ek hai graduation ke samay Shiv jise SSC crack karne se jyada tension rehti hai apne papa ke gusse ki. Dosara Shiv Delhi NCR ka upcoming SSC training institute chalata hai aur apne rival Khanna ke plans ka shikar hota rehta hai. Aieye dekhte hain kya hai in dono ka struggle?

Sam and Vidya have an intimate night together for the first time after they have got into a relationship. Sam is worried if the love between him and Vidya are real and if he can get used to sharing his personal space with Vidya! Watch the episode and find out more!

Bulaa liye tu jitne bhi gail badmaash tere

Me jit jaaun

Or bhaduuon ka kaaam
Pacche thokkar tezzz khane kaaakaaa

Mhara naam jo naa jaaane vo bhi leve naam rattt
Aaati deekh G wagon aaati aandhi te Tu bachhhhhh
Hoook
Chore haryaane wale gaad denge lathh
Hilee gaadi ghani chori baithi gail mhaare gachh
Kit bhaajega re bighey kille kulley saale att
6 feeet bheethar gaand devein  pavega na bach

Door te pehchana jaa manas  haryaane ka
Kaam mhaara haathi ka kutto ka bhonke jaane ka

 dum itna  raaaakhey  ad jyaa 
duniyaa pe hukum chalane ka
Bharkey chillum jalane kaa

kaaadu bhooot 
mere saaaale kaaa

snippet.title: Children 'mercilessly' killed by Hamas in Israel massacre - as Gaza is pummelled
snippet.description:
The unprecedented response promised by Israel in the wake of the weekend's atrocities has now well and truly clicked into gear.

Earlier, the Israeli military said it had secured the border with Gaza, which is now under the heaviest bombardment in its history

Meanwhile, residents in the Israeli city of Ashkelon - close to that border - were warned to take shelter by Hamas militants. 

A salvo of rocket fire then followed, the extent of the damage is still unclear.

Our Foreign Affairs Correspondent Secunder Kermani has been to the Kfar Aza kibbutz - one of those targeted by the militants on Saturday.

snippet.title: NEW! Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah | Ep 3899 | 11 Oct 2023 | Teaser
snippet.description:
Click here to subscribe to SAB: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC6-F5tO8uklgE9Zy8IvbdFw?sub_confirmation=1

Episode 3899: Goli Ka Naya Roop
--------------------------------------------------------
The people of Gokuldham are prepared to grant Bhakti's desire. Everyone is delighted when Bagha announces that Bawri will perform her devotional song as part of the celebration. Bhakti and her parents have also come to Gokuldham in anticipation of a visit from Ganapati. All the Gokuldham members are instructed to leave the area by Bhakti because, in her dream, Ganesha wants to practice Garba only with her. The whole Gokuldham community flees the area and hides inside the clubhouse. They let Goli know about the new plan adjustment. See the episode to find out what happens next!

Show Name – Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast –  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Nitish Bhaluni
Episodes No - 3899, 11 Oct 2023
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #sab #Latest #New #TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah2023 #tmkocfunnyepisodes #hindicomedy #comedyvideo #15yearsoftmkoc  

About the show: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

snippet.title: Ayalaan - Official Teaser | Sivakarthikeyan | A.R.Rahman | Rakul Preet Singh | R.Ravikumar
snippet.description:
Presenting the Official Teaser of "Ayalaan", Starring Sivakarthikeyan and Rakul Preet Singh in the lead roles. Directed by R. Ravikumar and produced by 24AM Studios & Music by A.R. Rahman.

Ayalaan is a science-fiction movie that promises to take you on a thrilling ride to space. The film features music composed by A.R. Rahman. Get ready to witness an epic adventure like never before with Ayalaan.

Starring - Sivakarthikeyan, Rakul Preet Singh, Karunakaran, Yogi Babu, Sharad Kelkar, Isha Koppikar, David Broughton-Davies, Banupriya, Balasaravanan, Kothandam, Rahul Madhav

snippet.title: Tejas Official Trailer | Kangana Ranaut | Sarvesh M | Ronnie S | In Cinemas 27 Oct
snippet.description:
Ab aasman se dushman pe waar hoga, ab jung ka elaan hoga! 

Ye woh Bharat hai, jisko chhedoge toh woh chhodega nahi!

#TejasTrailer out now. 

#Tejas In cinemas on 27th Oct. 

#BharatKoChhedogeTohChhodengeNahi

To the fearless warriors of the skies, a very Happy Indian Air Force Day! 
#IndianAirForceDay

Tejas is the story of the courageous female IAF officer - Tejas Gill, who’s determined to safeguard the nation at all costs. It’s India’s first air action film which also showcases India’s first indigenous fighter jet - Tejas. With the motto of ‘Bharat Ko Chhedoge, Toh Chhodenge Nahi’, the makers of Uri are set to bring another ultimate patriotic film!

snippet.description:
ഈ സപ്ലിമെന്റ് കഴിച്ചാൽ ചുളിവുകൾ മാറും,വെളുത്തു തുടുക്കും.രക്തയോട്ടം കൂടും  രക്തക്കുഴലുകൾ ക്ലീൻ ആകും /Dr Shimji /#baijusvlogs #drshimji #soukyam_Integrated_Medical_Centre
What is collagen?

Collagen is a protein that is found in all connective tissues in the body, including skin, bones, muscles, and tendons. It is the most abundant protein in the human body and is responsible for providing strength, structure, and elasticity to tissues.

Benefits of collagen

Collagen has many important benefits for the body, including:

Improves skin health: Collagen is a major component of the skin and plays a role in its strength, elasticity, and hydration. As we age, our bodies produce less collagen, which can lead to wrinkles, dry skin, and a loss of firmness. Collagen supplements and topical collagen products may help to improve skin health by reducing wrinkles, increasing hydration, and improving elasticity.
Relieves joint pain: Collagen is also found in cartilage, the tissue that cushions and protects our joints. As we age, the cartilage in our joints breaks down, which can lead to osteoarthritis and other joint problems. Collagen supplements may help to improve joint pain and stiffness by reducing inflammation and protecting the cartilage.
Improves bone health: Collagen is also important for bone health. It helps to strengthen bones and reduce the risk of osteoporosis. Studies have shown that collagen supplements may help to improve bone mineral density and reduce the risk of fractures in people with osteoporosis.
Promotes muscle growth: Collagen is also found in muscles and helps to support muscle growth and repair. Studies have shown that collagen supplements may help to increase muscle mass and strength in people who exercise regularly.
Reasons for collagen loss

There are a number of factors that can contribute to collagen loss, including:

Age: As we age, our bodies naturally produce less collagen.
Sun exposure: UV radiation from the sun can damage collagen and elastin, the proteins that give skin its elasticity.
Smoking: Smoking also damages collagen and elastin.
Poor diet: A diet low in protein, vitamin C, and other essential nutrients can also contribute to collagen loss.
Certain medical conditions: Some medical conditions, such as Ehlers-Danlos syndrome and osteogenesis imperfecta, can also cause collagen loss.
How to improve collagen production

There are a number of things you can do to improve collagen production and reduce the effects of collagen loss, including:

Eat a healthy diet: Eat a balanced diet that includes plenty of protein, vitamin C, and other essential nutrients. Good sources of protein include chicken, fish, lean beef, eggs, and dairy products. Good sources of vitamin C include citrus fruits, berries, and leafy green vegetables.
Protect your skin from the sun: Wear sunscreen with an SPF of 30 or higher every day, even on cloudy days.
Avoid smoking: Smoking damages collagen and elastin, so quitting smoking is one of the best things you can do for your skin health.
Get regular exercise: Exercise helps to promote collagen production and reduce inflammation. Aim for at least 30 minutes of moderate-intensity exercise most days of the week.
Consider collagen supplements: Collagen supplements may be helpful for people who are concerned about collagen loss. Collagen supplements are available in powder, capsule, and liquid form.
It is important to note that more research is needed to confirm the long-term safety and efficacy of collagen supplements. If you are considering taking collagen supplements, it is important to talk to your doctor first.

Kalank 2nd Last Episode 50 - [Eng Sub]  Hira Mani - Junaid Khan - Nazish Jahangir - Sami Khan - 11th October 2023 - HAR PAL GEO

"Kalank" follows Sara, a determined MBA graduate seeking a job while living with her parents. Her aunt perceives Sara as a threat to her daughter's wedding prospects, adding tension to their household. Meanwhile, Sara and her cousin Wahaj develop feelings for each other, leading to potential marriage plans.
However, Sara's faces a set of unfortunate events when she joins a new office and encounters Sarfaraz, a manager with malicious intent. He defames and disrespects her, triggering a series of troubles and crises in her professional and personal life.
As false accusations tarnish her reputation, Sara faces an uphill battle to prove her innocence. The drama intensifies as doubts and skepticism surround her. Will she be able to restore her credibility and regain her standing in society? Amidst the chaos, the future of Sara and Wahaj's relationship hangs in the balance. Will their love survive the challenges posed by external forces and family pressure?

snippet.title: Instant Soft Curd Dosa in Just 10 Mins | Spongy & Tasty Yogurt Dosa for Morning Breakfast
snippet.description:
Full Recipe: https://hebbarskitchen.com/sponge-dosa-recipe-curd-dosa-set-dosa/

@hebbarskitchenhindi @hebbarskitchenoriginals 

Sponge Dosa Recipe | Curd Dosa Recipe | Set Dosa Without Urad Dal with detailed photo and video recipe. A soft and sponge dosa prepared with rice and Poha which is mixed with curd which helps in fermentation. Note that in this dosa, there is no urad dal as compared to the traditional set dosa recipe. Hence it is an instant and easy dosa recipe that can be made within minutes while preserving the the traditional taste and values.

Sponge Dosa Recipe | Curd Dosa Recipe | Set Dosa Without Urad Dal with detailed photo and video recipe. Basically, an easy dosa or pancake-crepe recipe prepared with curd, and semolina with a porous and spongy texture. It is an ideal breakfast recipe but not limited to, that is traditionally served with chutney recipes, veg sagu, potato sagu, and sambar. Unlike the other popular dosa types, which are crisp and crunchy, curd dosa carries a soft and spongy texture hence the name.

#hebbarskitchen

Episode 3898: Goli Bana Ganesha
--------------------------------------------------------
Everyone eventually agrees that Goli will dress up as Ganapati and play Garba with Bhakti. Tapu Sena hires a cosmetic artist to turn Goli into Lord Ganesha. Everyone agrees to undertake this deed after midnight because other people would not grasp their true motivation and make fun of them, hurting Bhakti's feelings. Bhide phones Bhakti's parents to notify them of their plans and to ensure that Bhakti arrives at the location on time. Tapu Sena advises Goli the next morning on how to do the trick flawlessly. Bhide also instructs Goli that he must do the deed with zeal in order for Bhakti to believe in it.

snippet.description:
Thanks for watching Har Pal Geo. Please click here https://bit.ly/3rCBCYN to Subscribe and hit the bell icon to enjoy Top Pakistani Dramas and satisfy all your entertainment needs. Do you know Har Pal Geo is now available in the US? Share the News. Spread the word.

Kalank Last Episode 51 Teaser - 11th October 2023 - HAR PAL GEO

"Kalank" follows Sara, a determined MBA graduate seeking a job while living with her parents. Her aunt perceives Sara as a threat to her daughter's wedding prospects, adding tension to their household. Meanwhile, Sara and her cousin Wahaj develop feelings for each other, leading to potential marriage plans.
However, Sara's faces a set of unfortunate events when she joins a new office and encounters Sarfaraz, a manager with malicious intent. He defames and disrespects her, triggering a series of troubles and crises in her professional and personal life.
As false accusations tarnish her reputation, Sara faces an uphill battle to prove her innocence. The drama intensifies as doubts and skepticism surround her. Will she be able to restore her credibility and regain her standing in society? Amidst the chaos, the future of Sara and Wahaj's relationship hangs in the balance. Will their love survive the challenges posed by external forces and family pressure?

Written by: Edison Idrees Masih
Directed by: Mohsin Mirza
Produced by: Abdullah Kadwani & Asad Qureshi
Production House: 7th Sky Entertainment

Cast:
